OL,7,FThe Government has faced the wrath of
OL,8,FMPs over the "national scandal" of
OL,9,Fpeople being forced onto prepayment
OL,10,Fenergy meters ` after Grant Shapps
OL,11,Fasked suppliers to voluntarily end the
OL,12,Fpractice.
