OL,15,Fannounced on Sunday he would crack down
OL,16,Fon "trigger happy" firms forcing
OL,17,Fstruggling families onto the meters and
OL,18,Fleaving them without light or heat, but
OL,19,Ffell short of imposing a winter
OL,20,Fmoratorium in a letter to their chief
OL,21,Fexecutives.
